name: Aura ★ Bananas 002
description: I made this beautiful flier for my first ever performance in LA 🌐 check out a recap of the show on my Youtube: https://youtu.be/nPdsxoHZC3A + many thanks to Bananas Network for having me, I had so much fun! they've been running monthly community performances in Leimert Park for 14 years~ acts like Doja Cat and Anderson Paak have done shows with them in their early years. find out more about Bananas at instagram.com/bananasnetwork ♡ ★ buyers of this NFT get a free 4 pack of stickers designed by me.
